opennlp.tools.ml.model

类 FileEventStream

  • java.lang.Object
    • opennlp.tools.ml.model.FileEventStream
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    AutoCloseable, ObjectStream<Event>
    直接已知子类:
    RealValueFileEventStream

    public class FileEventStream
extends Object
implements ObjectStream<Event>
    Class for using a file of events as an event stream. The format of the file is one event perline with each line consisting of outcome followed by contexts (space delimited).

      • reset

        public void reset()
           throws IOException,
                  UnsupportedOperationException
        从接口复制的说明: ObjectStream
        Repositions the stream at the beginning and the previously seen object sequence will be repeated exactly. This method can be used to re-read the stream if multiple passes over the objects are required. The implementation of this method is optional.

        reset 在接口中 ObjectStream<Event>
